# UnoCSS Guardrails & Design Engine Law

> Binary FORBIDDEN/REQUIRED rules with zero exceptions unless explicitly stated. This file is the merged SSOT for UnoCSS generation safety and anti-hallucination constraints.

---

## GUARDRAIL 1 — Closed Shortcut Registry

Shortcuts are a **closed set**. If a shortcut is not in this list, it does not exist. Using or inventing it is a hallucination error.

### All Permitted Shortcuts

**Flex Layout**: `center` · `row-center` · `row-between` · `row-start` · `row-end` · `col-center` · `col-between` · `col-stretch` · `col-fill`

**Container Layout**: `layout-screen` · `layout-full` · `layout-container` · `layout-narrow`

**Positioning**: `absolute-center`

**Utility**: `scrollbar-none`

**Typography**: `text-no-wrap` · `text-ellipsis-1` · `text-ellipsis-2`

**Interaction**: `motion-lift` · `interaction-shrink` · `ring-focus-focus` · `interactive-card` · `interactive-item`

**Z-Index**: `z-base` · `z-content` · `z-layout` · `z-overlay` · `z-popover` · `z-toast`

**Material**: `material-solid` · `material-elevated` · `glass-card` · `glass-icon-box` · `glass-panel` · `glass-capsule` · `glass-shell`

**Documentation demo**: `demo-well` · `demo-stage`

**Code display**: `code-block` · `code-inline` · `code-preview`

> `glass-base` = internal primitive — DO NOT use directly.

**FORBIDDEN invented shortcuts (non-exhaustive)**:
`card-base` · `page-fill` · `content-wrap` · `panel-base` · `layout-stack` · `col-stack-*` · `density-*` · `fs-xs` · `surface-elevated` · `hover-bg-*` · `text-truncate`

