## GUARDRAIL 2 — No Shortcut + Its Own Expansion (N-1)

NEVER write a shortcut AND the atomic classes it expands into on the same element.

```html
<!-- FORBIDDEN -->
<div class="flex items-center justify-center center">
<div class="w-full h-full layout-full">
<div class="flex-1 min-h-0 flex flex-col overflow-hidden col-fill">
<div class="transition-all duration-md motion-lift">

<!-- CORRECT -->
<div class="center">
<div class="layout-full">
<div class="col-fill">
<div class="motion-lift">
```

**Self-check**: Does any shortcut in your class list expand into other classes also on the same element? Remove the expansion.

---

## GUARDRAIL 3 — No `flex` Prefix on Flex Shortcuts (N-2)

Flex shortcuts ALREADY contain `flex`. Prepending `flex`, `flex-row`, `flex-col`, `items-*`, `justify-*` is a duplicate.

```html
<!-- FORBIDDEN -->
<div class="flex row-between">
<div class="flex col-center">
<div class="flex flex-col col-fill">

<!-- CORRECT -->
<div class="row-between">
<div class="col-center">
<div class="col-fill">
```

