## GUARDRAIL 4 — Colors: Semantic Tokens ONLY

| FORBIDDEN | CORRECT |
|-----------|---------|
| `text-[#333]`, `bg-[#fff]`, `color: #ff0000` | `text-foreground`, `bg-background` |
| `text-red-500`, `bg-blue-200`, `text-gray-500`, `bg-slate-100` | `text-danger`, `bg-primary-light`, `text-muted-foreground`, `bg-muted` |
| `bg-white`, `bg-black`, `text-white`, `text-black` | `bg-background`, `text-foreground` |
| `dark:bg-gray-900`, `dark:text-white` | semantic tokens auto-respond to dark mode |
| `bg-white/50`, `bg-black/20` | `bg-background/50`, `bg-foreground/[0.04]` |
| `shadow-[0_4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]` | `shadow-sm`, `shadow-md` (no rgba) |

**Available semantic tokens**:
- Canvas: `bg-background` · `bg-card` · `bg-muted` · `bg-secondary` · `bg-popover`
- Text: `text-foreground` · `text-muted-foreground` · `text-card-foreground` · `text-secondary-foreground`
- Brand: `bg-primary` · `text-primary` · `bg-primary-hover` · `bg-primary-light`
- Status: `bg-danger` · `bg-warn` · `bg-success` · `bg-info`
- Sidebar: `bg-sidebar-background` · `text-sidebar-foreground` · `bg-sidebar-accent`

