## GUARDRAIL 6 — Z-Index: 6 Semantic Tokens Only

| FORBIDDEN | CORRECT |
|-----------|---------|
| `z-0`, `z-10`, `z-20`, `z-30`, `z-40`, `z-50` | `z-base` / `z-content` / `z-layout` |
| `z-[9999]`, `z-[100]`, `z-[999]` | `z-overlay` / `z-popover` / `z-toast` |
| `style="z-index: 100"` | use semantic token class |

Token reference: `z-base(0)` · `z-content(10)` · `z-layout(40)` · `z-overlay(50)` · `z-popover(60)` · `z-toast(100)`

If 6 tokens cannot express the stacking order: **restructure DOM stacking context**. Do NOT invent values.

