## GUARDRAIL 8 — Material Shortcut Mapping

| Surface | Required shortcut |
|---------|------------------|
| ProTable / Data Grid | `material-solid` |
| ProForm / Form containers | `material-elevated` |
| Dialogs / Modals / Dropdowns | `glass-panel` |
| Layout Sidebar / Header shell | `glass-shell` |
| Dashboard cards (glass style) | `glass-card` |
| Icon boxes (glass style) | `glass-icon-box` |
| Decorative floating pills | `glass-capsule` |
| Large cards (interactive) | `interactive-card` |
| List rows (interactive) | `interactive-item` |
| **DO NOT USE directly** | `glass-base` ← internal primitive |

**FORBIDDEN**: `glass-*` inside `<ProTable>`, virtual lists, or nested inside another `glass-*` element (GPU performance).

