## GUARDRAIL 9 — Transition Duration: Named Tokens

```
FORBIDDEN: duration-300, duration-200, duration-150, duration-500
CORRECT:   duration-xs (180ms) · duration-sm (280ms) · duration-md (320ms) · duration-lg (420ms)
```

